flowchart TB
    subgraph Fast[Fast automated check]
        direction LR
        Link[Portfolio link,<br/>profile, or credential file]:::person
        Signature[Issuer signature<br/>is valid]:::check
        Evidence[Linked work<br/>matches]:::check
        Status[Skill is active<br/>and current]:::check
        Pass[Show verified skill<br/>and policy summary]:::pass
        Link --> Signature --> Evidence --> Status --> Pass
    end

    Fail[Show changed, revoked,<br/>or superseded record]:::fail
    Detail[Optional human review:<br/>source, architecture, logs, demo]:::detail
    Fast -. any failed check .-> Fail
    Fast --> Detail

    classDef person fill:#f1eaff,stroke:#6941c6,color:#26164a,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef check fill:#e8f1ff,stroke:#2457a6,color:#10213a,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef pass fill:#d9f99d,stroke:#4d7c0f,color:#1a2e05,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef fail fill:#fee8e7,stroke:#b42318,color:#5d0e08,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef detail fill:#fff5dc,stroke:#a46b08,color:#4a3100,stroke-width:1.5px;
